</div></div></div><div class="anchorable docEntry" id="methods_eventnames_15"><div class="docEntryHeader"><code class="inline-code-block"><a href="#methods_eventnames_15" class="anchor-link" aria-label="Anchor" tabindex="-1">#</a><a class="font-bold font-lg link" href="../.././events/~/EventEmitter.eventNames">eventNames</a><span class="font-medium">()<span>: <span>Array</span>&lt;<span>(<span><span>string</span><span> | </span><span>symbol</span></span>)<span> & </span><a href="../.././events/~/Key2" class="link">Key2</a>&lt;<span>unknown</span><span>, </span><a href="#type_param_T" class="link">T</a>&gt;</span>&gt;</span></span></code> </div><div class="max-w-[75ch]"><div data-color-mode="dark" data-light-theme="light" data-dark-theme="dark" class="markdown-body"><p>Returns an array listing the events for which the emitter has registered
